# Technical Stack
Referenced in: [001-project-overview.mdc](001-project-overview.mdc)

## Framework & Language
- Framework: Next.js 15 (App Router)
- Language: TypeScript
- Styling: Tailwind CSS, tailwind-merge, clsx

## UI Components
- Library: Radix UI
- Pattern: Shadcn UI
- Icons: Lucide React
- Charts: Recharts

## Backend & Auth
- Platform: Firebase v11
- Auth: Firebase Auth
- Database: Firestore
- Validation: Zod + React Hook Form

## AI & External
- SDK: Genkit (Google AI SDK)

